text: Sandra Raluca Izbaşa () (born June 18, 1990) is a Romanian gymnast. She has won two Olympic gold medals, at the floor event at the 2008 Olympics and at the vault event at the 2012 Olympics.Athletes :: Show . Fig.lx2.sportcentric.com.
